message.text:
thank you to one of my blockmates who bravely pointed out the attitude of our prof, yes #that #prof. she’s not really terror, she’s more than disrespectful. imagine, she had tantrums for almost 10 minutes just because one of my blockmates got confused and answered wrong. on top of that, some of us were lagging, and she even scared us by saying she would already encode our grades and start our sem break dahil lang mahina signal tapos pinapaulit lang yung tanong? 

gusto niya ng respeto pero siya mismo hindi magawa sa amin, how funny diba? it should be give and take.
